          <title>Tampa Bay Rays to play 2025 season at Yankees' spring training field</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Tampa Bay Rays will play their 2025 home games at the New York Yankees' nearby spring training ballpark amid uncertainty about the future of hurricane-damaged Tropicana Field, Rays executives told The Associated Press.]]></description>
